<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Ziziphus</i> <i>obtusifolia</i> is dominant in the shrub canopy with <i>Atriplex</i> <i>canescens</i>, <i>Ephedra</i> <i>californica</i>, <i>Hyptis</i> <i>emoryi</i> and <i>Senegalia</i> <i>greggii</i>. Emergent trees may be present at low cover, including <i>Olneya</i> <i>tesota</i>. </div>
</div>

        
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Shrubs < 3 m; canopy is intermittent. </div>
</div>

        
